# nav-telemator

Contribution for Telemator additions in NAV

## Local files

`etc/python/local_settings.py`

    LOCAL_SETTINGS = True
    from nav.django.settings import *

    TEMPLATE_LOADERS = (
        'django.template.loaders.app_directories.Loader',
        'django.template.loaders.filesystem.Loader'
    )

    INSTALLED_APPS += (
        'navtelemator',
    )

`etc/python/local_urls.py`

    from django.conf.urls import url, patterns
    from navtelemator.views.circuit import get_security_state_metric
    urlpatterns = patterns(
        '',
        url(r'^ajax/open/navuds/getstatemetric', get_security_state_metric,
            name='contrib-nav-uds-metric'),
    )

## Developement

`hg clone ssh://hg@bitbucket.org/bredal/nav-uds`

### Build

`python ./setup.py build sdist`

### Install

`pip install dist/*`

### Uninstall

`pip uninstall nav-contrib-telemator`
